entry.title: Covid Boosters Aren't Reaching People Who Want Them
entry.content: Public-health experts said setbacks related to scheduling and insurance coverage risk discouraging people from getting the shots.

entry.title: Work Permits Won't Be Silver Bullet for New York Migrant Crisis
entry.content: Biden’s move to grant work authorization to Venezuelans addresses only part of the problem of overrun cities—and could lure more migrants to come.
